title: *PATREON PREVIEW* AMA: The Throwing Fits Biopic Pt. I
description:
The Core Four are back on the hot seat, answering your questions in the first half of our latest AMA. Topics include, but are not limited to: TF FAQs, 9/11, copping jawnz vs. paying rent, The Post Sneaker World, wine, podcasting professionally, silk, getting married, dying, fucking with your boy’s vision, swagless homies, groms and much more on this Patreon-exclusive boyz only edition of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
